### LEARNING AND DEVELOPMENT

#### User Story E12: Learning Resource Access
**As an Employee, I want to access relevant learning resources so that I can develop skills identified in my feedback and goals.**

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Discover learning resources related to development areas
- Access training courses, articles, and educational content
- Track completion of learning activities
- Apply learned skills and document implementation
- Share learning insights with team members

**Dashboard Features:**
- Personalized learning resource recommendations
- Learning activity catalog with search and filtering
- Progress tracking for courses and training programs
- Knowledge application documentation tools
- Learning sharing and discussion forums

#### User Story E13: Training and Certification Tracking
**As an Employee, I want to track my training and certifications so that I can demonstrate my professional development.**

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Log completed training programs and certifications
- Track certification expiration dates and renewal requirements
- Document learning outcomes and skill applications
- Share achievements with manager and team
- Plan future training based on career goals

**Dashboard Features:**
- Training and certification portfolio
- Expiration date tracking with renewal reminders
- Achievement sharing and recognition system
- Learning outcome documentation templates
- Future training planning and budget tracking

### PERFORMANCE INSIGHTS AND ANALYTICS

#### User Story E14: Personal Performance Analytics
**As an Employee, I want to view my performance trends so that I can understand my growth patterns and areas for focus.**

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- View performance trends over time
- Compare current performance to previous periods
- Understand rating patterns and feedback themes
- Identify consistent strengths and development areas
- Set data-driven improvement targets

**Dashboard Features:**
- Personal performance dashboard with trend analysis
- Feedback sentiment analysis and themes
- Performance comparison tools (self vs manager ratings)
- Strengths and development area trend tracking
- Goal achievement rate visualization

#### User Story E15: Feedback Quality and Engagement
**As an Employee, I want to understand the quality of feedback I receive and give so that I can improve my participation in the feedback process.**

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Track the completeness and depth of feedback received
- Monitor my own feedback giving quality and timeliness
- Understand my engagement level in feedback processes
- Receive suggestions for improving feedback participation
- Compare my feedback patterns to organizational standards

**Dashboard Features:**
- Feedback quality metrics and scoring
- Participation rate tracking and benchmarking
- Feedback giving and receiving balance analysis
- Improvement suggestions for feedback quality
- Recognition for high-quality feedback participation

